verses.text:
All you that are weary and sad, come,
And you that are cheerful and glad, come;
In robes of humility clad, come;
The Saviour invites you to-day.
In robes of humility, come to-day.

Acquaint thyself quickly, O sinner, with God;
And joy, like the sunshine, shall beam on thy road;
And peace, like the dewdrop, shall fall on thy head;
And sleep, like an angel, shall visit thy bed.
